---
title: Golden Coconut Pork & Veggie Udon Noodles with Crushed Peanuts & Coriander
description: Everything is glittering and golden tonight, with ropes of pork udon noodles coiled in a coconutty broth. It’s brimming with delicious pops of veggies like baby broccoli and carrot. All you need is a sprinkle of peanuts to make this dish shine!
